            <title>[MJAVADOC-183] Aggregate javadoc does not process the src/main/javadoc directories</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MJAVADOC-183</link>
                <project id="12317529" key="MJAVADOC">Maven Javadoc Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
